{"word":"Adam","slug":"adam","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Adam</b> <a href=\"#/H121\">H121</a><br/><a href=\"#/G76\">G76</a> <br/> 1. The first man<br/> - Creation of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=1&verse=28'>Gen 1:28</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=2&verse=7'>Gen 2:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=46&chapter=15&verse=45'>1Co 15:45</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=54&chapter=2&verse=13'>1Ti 2:13</a> <br/> - History of, before he sinned<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=1&verse=30'>Gen 1:30</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=2&verse=25'>Gen 2:25</a> <br/> - Temptation and sin of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=3'>Gen 3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=18&chapter=31&verse=33'>Job 31:33</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=43&verse=27'>Isa 43:27</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=28&chapter=6&verse=7'>Hos 6:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=45&chapter=5&verse=21'>Rom 5:21</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=54&chapter=2&verse=14'>1Ti 2:14</a> <br/> - Subsequent history of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=3&verse=24'>Gen 3:24</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=4&verse=2'>Gen 4:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=4&verse=25'>Gen 4:25</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=5&verse=5'>Gen 5:5</a> <br/> - His death<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=5&verse=5'>Gen 5:5</a> <br/> - Progenitor of the human race<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=32&verse=8'>Deu 32:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=39&chapter=2&verse=10'>Mal 2:10</a> <br/> - Brought sin into the world<br/> <a href='https